WEBVTT

1
00:00:29.950 --> 00:00:31.510
I'm glad you decided to come.

2
00:00:31.910 --> 00:00:36.020
Note... or rather. Arthur Leywin.

3
00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:40.530
You were the one who defeated
the Elder Woods. yes?

4
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:45.610
He's strong. and dangerous.

5
00:00:46.650 --> 00:00:48.600
More than anyone I've ever encountered.

6
00:02:19.510 --> 00:02:24.510
#12 The King Enrolls.

7
00:02:21.740 --> 00:02:25.380
If I'm the target...
is Lucas behind this?

8
00:02:26.260 --> 00:02:27.880
Who sent you?

9
00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:34.257
That fledgling you have in
mind has served his purpose.

10
00:02:34.340 --> 00:02:36.137
He's not lying.

11
00:02:36.220 --> 00:02:38.470
Lucas is nothing compared
to whoever this is.

12
00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:41.597
The Wykes family has provided some value.

13
00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:45.250
but now there's a matter that
takes greater precedence.

14
00:02:45.580 --> 00:02:50.650
considering a single adventurer was
able to defeat the Elder Woods.

15
00:02:55.880 --> 00:03:01.790
Arthur Leywin... his father.
Reynolds. and his mother. Alice.

16
00:03:02.040 --> 00:03:07.717
Born 12 years ago. Awakened his
mana core at the tender age of two.

17
00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:10.730
before moving to Xyrus City.

18
00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:15.807
His family was attacked by bandits
en route. leading to his disappearance.

19
00:03:15.890 --> 00:03:18.940
He reunited with his family
three years later.

20
00:03:19.370 --> 00:03:21.430
He registered with the
adventurer's guild at age ten.

21
00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.560
under the alias of "Note."

22
00:03:23.930 --> 00:03:28.690
He had a stint as an adventurer at
the side of Jasmine Flamesworth.

23
00:03:29.310 --> 00:03:33.070
Your parents were members of
the Twinhorns as well. yes?

24
00:03:33.310 --> 00:03:35.820
He retraced the path I've taken.

25
00:03:36.300 --> 00:03:38.780
You certainly seem knowledgeable about me.

26
00:03:39.270 --> 00:03:40.487
Are you a fan. by any chance?

27
00:03:40.570 --> 00:03:41.830
Don't bother.

28
00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:46.830
I'm not here to fight. I'm just curious.

29
00:03:47.230 --> 00:03:51.707
The guild records say Note...
that is to say. you.

30
00:03:51.790 --> 00:03:54.627
defeated the Elder Woods by yourself.

31
00:03:54.710 --> 00:03:56.090
How did you manage that?

32
00:03:56.680 --> 00:03:58.747
Brald and the others were there. too.

33
00:03:58.830 --> 00:04:01.607
He wasn't strong enough to
manage something like that.

34
00:04:01.690 --> 00:04:03.137
What makes you so sure?

35
00:04:03.220 --> 00:04:06.160
I have a very good grasp
of his strength.

36
00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:10.330
since I was the one who sent him there.

37
00:04:12.900 --> 00:04:13.980
I see.

38
00:04:15.530 --> 00:04:16.770
It was you.

39
00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.280
You have to pay.

40
00:04:29.450 --> 00:04:30.510
What was that?

41
00:04:37.270 --> 00:04:39.050
Sonic magic?!

42
00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:41.000
That's only the beginning.

43
00:04:54.650 --> 00:04:57.080
The interval between his
casting is so short.

44
00:04:57.510 --> 00:04:59.610
and he has access to a myriad of elements.

45
00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:02.860
Is this some form of magic I don't know?

46
00:05:10.190 --> 00:05:12.090
But with this timing...

47
00:05:33.980 --> 00:05:39.667
Your swordplay and mana control could
both be described as first-rate.

48
00:05:39.750 --> 00:05:45.990
Yet. there's still more. I can tell.
having seen many a mana beast before.

49
00:05:46.390 --> 00:05:50.760
The power that inhabits your
mana core is... one of a kind.

50
00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:57.750
It was you who killed the
Elder Woods. Arthur Leywin.

51
00:06:00.100 --> 00:06:02.510
You said you've seen many mana beasts.

52
00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:05.927
I take it you're behind the
strangeness in the Beast Glades?

53
00:06:06.010 --> 00:06:10.540
It was a very convenient location
to test the results of my research.

54
00:06:11.030 --> 00:06:12.520
Nothing more.

55
00:06:12.860 --> 00:06:18.720
Now. tell me... how did you
defeat the Elder Woodsâ€”

56
00:06:26.070 --> 00:06:27.450
You little wretch.

57
00:06:28.780 --> 00:06:31.540
You've been holding back.

58
00:06:31.750 --> 00:06:34.307
I'm not foolish enough
to expose myself to a foe

59
00:06:34.390 --> 00:06:36.540
I don't know the identity or objective of.

60
00:06:38.270 --> 00:06:41.940
Now. answer me. What are you after?

61
00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:43.300
Youâ€”

62
00:06:47.230 --> 00:06:51.310
I wouldn't shout too much.
Considering where you chose to meet...

63
00:06:55.030 --> 00:06:57.560
I doubt you want to draw much attention.

64
00:06:58.810 --> 00:07:01.570
What in the world are you?

65
00:07:12.910 --> 00:07:14.090
I want answers.

66
00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:20.220
There's no doubt of it.
You beat the Elder Woods.

67
00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:25.810
I suppose my curiosity has led me
to catch a tiger by its tail.

68
00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:31.627
My objective is control over mana beasts.

69
00:07:31.710 --> 00:07:34.767
I'm looking to complete the
spell necessary for that.

70
00:07:34.850 --> 00:07:38.507
I can already control
anything A-class and below.

71
00:07:38.590 --> 00:07:43.870
But S-class mana beasts
are still beyond me.

72
00:07:44.260 --> 00:07:47.140
You weren't controlling the Elder Woods?

73
00:07:49.180 --> 00:07:53.700
The wills of S-class beasts
keep me from taking control.

74
00:07:55.070 --> 00:07:59.220
So I took measures to remove their will!

75
00:08:04.380 --> 00:08:07.257
I wasn't in control of the Elder Woods.

76
00:08:07.340 --> 00:08:12.137
But by removing its will. I was
able to broadly direct its actions.

77
00:08:12.220 --> 00:08:16.530
Directing it to kill anyone
who entered the cave!

78
00:08:17.830 --> 00:08:19.667
This is a strengthening potion

79
00:08:19.750 --> 00:08:24.147
that explosively increases
mana at the cost of lost will.

80
00:08:24.230 --> 00:08:28.040
It's my first time using it on a human.
Desperate times. you understand.

81
00:08:29.300 --> 00:08:33.990
My anonymity is too precious to me!

82
00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:39.120
He's too dangerous! I have to
stop him from getting away!

83
00:10:09.230 --> 00:10:10.857
What's going on out there?!

84
00:10:10.940 --> 00:10:12.260
Mom...

85
00:10:14.630 --> 00:10:16.860
Arthur... Where's Arthur?

86
00:10:19.390 --> 00:10:21.270
Elijah. have you seen Arthur?

87
00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:23.770
He's missing?!

88
00:10:33.630 --> 00:10:36.530
People I care about live beyond here.

89
00:10:37.660 --> 00:10:38.910
I don't care who you are.

90
00:10:39.530 --> 00:10:41.290
You will not pass!

91
00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:29.290
How about this?!

92
00:11:51.780 --> 00:11:55.317
He has the physical abilities
of an S-class mana beast.

93
00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:58.160
And on top of that. he can cast magic...

94
00:11:58.670 --> 00:12:00.420
with an incredible level of output.

95
00:12:03.220 --> 00:12:06.160
Neither my swords or spells
are having any effect!

96
00:12:07.580 --> 00:12:08.670
What else?

97
00:12:10.830 --> 00:12:12.300
What else can I do?

98
00:12:14.170 --> 00:12:15.420
Damn itâ€”

99
00:12:45.830 --> 00:12:47.200
I see.

100
00:12:47.910 --> 00:12:49.960
Then. loss...

101
00:12:50.500 --> 00:12:52.600
To deprive others...

102
00:12:54.550 --> 00:12:56.450
This is what it feels like.

103
00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:08.830
If this ending...

104
00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:13.230
is the penance for my previous life.

105
00:13:13.710 --> 00:13:15.250
then there's nothing I...

106
00:13:27.820 --> 00:13:28.500
Grandma?

107
00:13:29.030 --> 00:13:36.380
Arthur. What will you do with
that power. if you get stronger?

108
00:13:41.940 --> 00:13:46.640
I'll protect...
the people... I care about.

109
00:14:08.410 --> 00:14:09.540
Here I come!

110
00:14:27.850 --> 00:14:30.930
Absolute Zero!

111
00:14:58.140 --> 00:15:02.480
I have taken... so many lives.

112
00:15:03.380 --> 00:15:05.470
and brought so many nations to ruin.

113
00:15:06.630 --> 00:15:10.470
But even then... in spite of thatâ€”

114
00:15:11.210 --> 00:15:12.440
Arthur...

115
00:15:23.850 --> 00:15:26.610
I will not be beaten!

116
00:16:13.040 --> 00:16:14.490
Enough of you!

117
00:16:29.640 --> 00:16:32.990
"Don't let your heart fill
with hatred and rage."

118
00:16:33.980 --> 00:16:39.150
How many times have I broken
my promise to you already?

119
00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:43.220
Forgive me. Sylvia.

120
00:16:45.350 --> 00:16:48.040
I guess I shouldn't stick around here.

121
00:17:00.920 --> 00:17:02.380
You look a mess.

122
00:17:02.660 --> 00:17:05.380
You?! We've got bigger concerns!

123
00:17:05.670 --> 00:17:07.527
Listen to me! That boyâ€”

124
00:17:07.610 --> 00:17:10.127
The city is a mess.

125
00:17:10.210 --> 00:17:12.677
Covering it up is going to
be an absolute nightmare.

126
00:17:12.760 --> 00:17:14.640
That! Doesn't! Matter!

127
00:17:14.950 --> 00:17:20.017
That's no ordinary beast inside the boy!
Its power surpasses S-class!

128
00:17:20.100 --> 00:17:23.020
Like something of legend or mythologyâ€”

129
00:17:24.120 --> 00:17:27.310
Wait. No. but that's...

130
00:17:27.670 --> 00:17:29.890
Yet. it has to be.

131
00:17:30.520 --> 00:17:33.150
He has a dragon'sâ€”

132
00:17:38.630 --> 00:17:40.660
Wh-Why?

133
00:17:46.730 --> 00:17:48.420
The day after the attack.

134
00:17:49.260 --> 00:17:54.680
I was barely able to avoid giving
Alice and Eleanor any real answers.

135
00:17:55.620 --> 00:17:57.930
I had a little bit of help.

136
00:17:58.680 --> 00:18:00.937
"A mana beast escaped and ran amuck."

137
00:18:01.020 --> 00:18:03.690
"Academy Director Cynthia
assisted in its recapture."

138
00:18:04.170 --> 00:18:06.000
That was the story that was told.

139
00:18:08.190 --> 00:18:11.190
Reynolds didn't ask questions.

140
00:18:11.930 --> 00:18:15.950
Possibly because he'd realized something.

141
00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:22.837
I returned to the ruins of the church.
hoping to find some clues.

142
00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:24.460
but there was nothing.

143
00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:29.460
My memories of that day are
something I will never forget.

144
00:18:30.100 --> 00:18:33.790
but they will be buried by other
memories as time goes by.

145
00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:48.730
Time spent away from battle.
with the people I care about...

146
00:18:49.060 --> 00:18:52.490
was more valuable than
anything I could imagine.

147
00:19:02.630 --> 00:19:04.250
Sonic magic...

148
00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:06.010
Was that her?

149
00:19:19.610 --> 00:19:26.187
You who will become the future leaders.
scholars. and movers of Dicathen...

150
00:19:26.270 --> 00:19:29.987
I welcome you to our humble academy.

151
00:19:30.070 --> 00:19:33.250
I am Cynthia Goodsky. the director.

152
00:19:33.820 --> 00:19:36.570
And I get the feeling this
will be a very special year.

153
00:19:36.860 --> 00:19:41.757
There has never been a class with
so many elves and dwarves enrolled.

154
00:19:41.840 --> 00:19:43.537
for one thing.

155
00:19:43.620 --> 00:19:46.477
And I can imagine no
better way to greet you.

156
00:19:46.560 --> 00:19:50.130
than with a word from your
student body's representatives;

157
00:19:50.810 --> 00:19:54.680
a round of applause. please.
for your student council.

158
00:21:43.120 --> 00:21:43.990
Sylvie!

159
00:21:57.710 --> 00:22:03.470
"Come along now. It's safe.
You can go home."

160
00:22:05.760 --> 00:22:09.890
"I don't think so. A tree golem could
eat a child like me in no time."

161
00:22:11.050 --> 00:22:12.770
"Then. do you know which
direction you came from?"

162
00:22:12.990 --> 00:22:17.520
"Can't say that I do. I was chasing
some bugs and then I got lost."

163
00:22:19.690 --> 00:22:21.100
"Okay. then."

164
00:22:21.900 --> 00:22:24.767
"What's your name?"

165
00:22:24.850 --> 00:22:27.530
"It's Tessia. Tessia Eralith."

166
00:22:27.950 --> 00:22:29.540
"What's yours?"

167
00:22:29.880 --> 00:22:31.540
"Arthur Leywin."

168
00:22:34.520 --> 00:22:38.087
It's funny how we both remember
so much of what we said.

169
00:22:38.170 --> 00:22:39.300
Tell me about it.

170
00:22:40.060 --> 00:22:42.457
It's been a while. Arthur.

171
00:22:42.540 --> 00:22:44.770
It really has. Tess.
